零知識證明用於{{link-en|小零幣協議|Zerocoin protocol|小零幣}}與大零幣協議中，最終於2016年發展成{{link-en|小零幣|Zcoin}}<ref name="Hellwig 2020"/>（2020年改稱{{le|飛熔幣|Firo (cryptocurrency)}}）<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hurst |first1=Samantha |title=Zcoin Announces Rebranding to New Name & Ticker "Firo" |url=https://www.crowdfundinsider.com/2020/10/168504-zcoin-announces-rebranding-to-new-name-ticker-firo/ |publisher=Crowdfund Insider |access-date=4 November 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101141745/https://www.crowdfundinsider.com/2020/10/168504-zcoin-announces-rebranding-to-new-name-ticker-firo/ |archive-date=30 October 2020}}</ref>和[[Zcash|大零幣]]兩種[[加密貨幣|加密貨幣]]。小零幣內置有[[加密貨幣混幣器|混幣]]模型，以確保匿名，且該模型無需信任任何對等用戶或中央集權混幣者。<ref name="Hellwig 2020"/>用戶可以用另一種基準幣交易，也可以將該幣賣出買入小零幣。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Bonneau|first1=J|last2=Miller|first2=A|last3=Clark|first3=J|last4=Narayanan|first4=A|date=2015|title=SoK: Research Perspectives and Challenges for Bitcoin and Cryptocurrencies|url=https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7163021|journal=2015 IEEE Symposium on Security and Privacy|location=San Jose, Carlifornia|pages=104–121|access-date=2021-11-21|archive-date=2022-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220210120938/https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7163021|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|118}}大零幣協議的模型也類似（該變式稱為{{link-en|非交互式零知識證明|Non-interactive zero-knowledge proof}}）<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ben-Sasson|first1=Eli|last2=Chiesa|first2=Alessandro|last3=Garman|first3=Christina|last4=Green|first4=Matthew|last5=Miers|first5=Ian|last6=Tromer|first6=Eran|last7=Virza|first7=Madars|title=Zerocash: Decentralized Anonymous Payments from Bitcoin|url=http://zerocash-project.org/media/pdf/zerocash-extended-20140518.pdf|publisher=IEEE|access-date=26 January 2016|date=18 May 2014|archive-date=2022-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220208224145/http://zerocash-project.org/media/pdf/zerocash-extended-20140518.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而且可以掩蓋交易額，但小零幣則不能。大零幣的交易數據如此隱密，所以與小零幣相比，較不易受到隱私{{le|計時攻擊|Timing attack}}。不過，此層額外隱私，可能導致不能追蹤假幣，倘因此造成大零幣供給的超通漲，可能無法偵測到。<ref name="Hellwig 2020">{{cite book |last1=Hellwig |first1=Daniel |last2=Karlic |first2=Goran |last3=Huchzermeier |first3=Arnd |title=Build your own blockchain - A practical guide to distributed ledger technology |date=3 May 2020 |publisher=SpringerLink |isbn=9783030401429 |page=112 |url=https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-40142-9_5 |access-date=3 December 2020 |chapter=Privacy and Anonymity |doi=10.1007/978-3-030-40142-9_5 |archive-date=2021-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121183527/https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-40142-9_5 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.technologyreview.com/s/609448/a-mind-bending-cryptographic-trick-promises-to-take-blockchains-mainstream|title=A mind-bending cryptographic trick promises to take blockchains mainstream|last=Orcutt|first=Mike|work=MIT Technology Review|access-date=2017-12-18|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815193321/https://www.technologyreview.com/s/609448/a-mind-bending-cryptographic-trick-promises-to-take-blockchains-mainstream/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，防彈證明（{{lang|en|bulletproofs}}）面世。其改進自非交互式零知識證明，不再需要可信的安裝環境。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bünz |first1=B |last2=Bootle |first2=D |last3=Boneh |first3=A |title=Bulletproofs: Short Proofs for Confidential Transactions and More |journal=IEEE Symposium on Security and Privacy |date=2018 |pages=315–334 |doi=10.1109/SP.2018.00020 |url=https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8418611 |access-date=3 December 2020 |location=San Francisco, Carlifornia |isbn=978-1-5386-4353-2 |s2cid=3337741 |doi-access=free |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121103156/https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8418611/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>其後，實作成「結舌」協議（{{lang|en|Mimblewimble protocol}}，{{lang|en|Grin}}和{{lang|en|Beam}}兩種加密幣皆出自該協議）和[[门罗币|门罗币]]。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Odendaal |first1=Hansie |last2=Sharrock |first2=Cayle |last3=Heerden |first3=SW |title=Bulletproofs and Mimblewimble |url=https://tlu.tarilabs.com/cryptography/bulletproofs-and-mimblewimble/MainReport.html#current-and-past-efforts |publisher=Tari Labs University |access-date=3 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929160834/https://tlu.tarilabs.com/cryptography/bulletproofs-and-mimblewimble/MainReport.html |archive-date=29 September 2020}}</ref>2019年，飛熔幣實作{{link-en|知識證明|Proof of knowledge|Sigma協議}}，是對應小零幣協議無可信環境的改進。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Andrew |first1=Munro |title=Zcoin cryptocurrency introduces zero knowledge proofs with no trusted set-up |url=https://www.finder.com.au/zcoin-cryptocurrency-introduces-zero-knowledge-proofs-with-no-trusted-setup |access-date=30 July 2019 |publisher=Finder Australia |date=30 July 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730210721/https://www.finder.com.au/zcoin-cryptocurrency-introduces-zero-knowledge-proofs-with-no-trusted-setup |archive-date=30 July 2019}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite journal |last1=Groth |first1=J |last2=Kohlweiss |first2=M |title=One-Out-of-Many Proofs: Or How to Leak a Secret and Spend a Coin |journal=Annual International Conference on the Theory and Applications of Cryptographic Techniques |series=Lecture Notes in Computer Science |date=14 April 2015 |volume=9057 |pages=253–280 |doi=10.1007/978-3-662-46803-6_9 |publisher=EUROCRYPT 2015 |location=Berlin, Heidelberg|isbn=978-3-662-46802-9 }}</ref>同年，飛熔幣引入萊蘭托斯協議<!-- [[WP:外語譯音表/希臘語|WP:外語譯音表/希臘語]]按Λήλαντος譯-->（{{lang|en|Lelantus protocol}}），更自Sigma協議改進，隱去交易的源頭與金額。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Aram |first1=Jivanyan |title=Lelantus: Towards Confidentiality and Anonymity of Blockchain Transactions from Standard Assumptions |journal=Cryptology ePrint Archive |date=7 April 2019 |issue=Report 373 |url=https://eprint.iacr.org/2019/373 |access-date=14 April 2019 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414131649/https://eprint.iacr.org/2019/373 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 沿革 ==
零知識證明最早由[[莎菲·戈德瓦塞尔|莎菲·戈德瓦塞尔]]、[[希爾維奧·米卡利|希爾維奧·米卡利]]、{{link-en|查爾斯·拉克福|Charles Rackoff}}<!--沿用[[蒙特利爾工程學院大屠殺|蒙特利爾工程學院大屠殺]]所採譯名-->三人於1985年發表，論文題為{{單雙書名號轉換|交互式證明系統的知識複雜度}}。<ref name="knowledgecomplexity" />該論文引入[[交互式证明系统|交互式证明系统]]的{{le|IP (複雜度)|IP (complexity)|'''IP'''複雜度類}}，並構想出「知識複雜度」概念，衡量證明過程中，由證明者傳遞予驗證者的知識量。三人亦給出首個具體問題的零知識證明，即零知識地證明某數不是模 ''m'' 的[[二次剩余|二次剩余]]。連同{{link-en|鲍鲍伊·拉茲洛|László Babai}}<!--姓Babai按《世界人名翻译大辞典·上》譯-->與{{link-en|什洛莫·莫蘭|Shlomo Moran}}<!--按[[什洛莫·本哈伊姆|什洛莫·本哈伊姆]]和[[達夫·莫蘭|達夫·莫蘭]]拼成-->的另一篇論文，戈-米-拉三氏的論文發明了交互式證明系統。為此，五人同獲1993年首屆[[哥德尔奖|哥德尔奖]]。

引述戈-米-拉三氏：

<blockquote>
該額外知識基本為0的情況尤其值得關注。我等證明，可以交互地證明某數非模 ''m'' 的二次剩餘，而釋出零額外知識。其出奇之處是，若不給定 ''m'' 的分解，則無高效算法判別某數是否模 ''m'' 的二次剩餘。更甚者，任何已知的[[NP_(複雜度)|'''NP''']]證明皆要表明 ''m'' 的質因數分解。這就表明，在證明過程中添加互動，可能減少證明某定理所必須交流的知識。
{{註|原文作 "Of particular interest is the case where this additional knowledge is essentially 0 and we show that [it] is possible to interactively prove that a number is quadratic non residue mod ''m'' releasing 0 additional knowledge. This is surprising as no efficient algorithm for deciding quadratic residuosity mod ''m'' is known when ''m''’s factorization is not given. Moreover, all known ''NP'' proofs for this problem exhibit the prime factorization of ''m''. This indicates that adding interaction to the proving process, may decrease the amount of knowledge that must be communicated in order to prove a theorem."}}
</blockquote>

二次非剩餘問題既有'''[[NP_(複雜度)|NP]]'''算法又有'''[[反NP|反NP]]'''算法，故位處'''NP'''與'''反NP'''兩類之交集中。其後找到有零知識證明的若干個問題，亦具同樣的性質，例如{{link-en|歐迪·戈德賴希|Oded Goldreich}}<!--譯名依[[歐迪·費爾|歐迪·費爾]]拼[[彼得·戈德賴希|彼得·戈德賴希]]-->未經正式出版的證明系統，可以驗證某數（為兩個未知質數之積）不是{{link-en|布盧姆整數|Blum integer}}，即並非兩個模4餘3的質數之積。<ref>{{cite journal |first=Oded |last=Goldreich |title=A zero-knowledge proof that a two-prime moduli is not a Blum integer |journal=Unpublished Manuscript |year=1985 }}</ref>

{{link-en|歐迪·戈德賴希|Oded Goldreich}}、[[希爾維奧·米卡利|希爾維奧·米卡利]]、[[阿维·威格森|阿维·威格森]]更進一步證明，假定存在無懈可擊的加密法，則可以造出[[图着色问题|三色圖着色問題]]的零知識證明系統，而該問題本身為[[NP完全|NP完全]]。又因為每個'''NP'''問題都可以高效化歸成該NP完全問題，所以在前述假定下，所有'''NP'''問題皆有零知識證明。<ref>{{cite journal |first1=Oded |last1=Goldreich |first2=Silvio |last2=Micali |first3=Avi |last3=Wigderson |title=Proofs that yield nothing but their validity |journal=Journal of the ACM |volume=38 |issue=3 |pages=690–728 |doi=10.1145/116825.116852 |year=1991 |citeseerx=10.1.1.420.1478 |s2cid=2389804 }}</ref>需要該假定的原因是，正如[[#大圖的哈密頓環|前節範例]]，需要有秘諾的手段。若存在[[單向函數|單向函數]]，則的確有牢不可破的加密法。此為廣泛引用的充分條件。另外也可能有物理方法實作。

更上一層樓，他們亦證明，{{le|圖不同構問題|graph nonisomorphism problem}}，即{{link-en|圖同構問題|graph isomorphism problem}}之{{link-en|補 (複雜度)|complement (complexity)|補}}，有零知識證明。該問題已知屬於'''反NP'''，但未知是否屬於'''NP'''或其他實際可行的複雜度類。更一般地，{{link-en|羅素·英帕利亞佐|Russell Impagliazzo}}<!--沿用[[聖艾智德團體|聖艾智德團體]]中Marco Impagliazzo的譯名-->、{{link-en|莫迪凱·容|Moti Yung}}{{譯名請求}}二人，與米高·本-奧爾（{{lang|en|Michael Ben-Or}}）及同事，兩組證明：同樣假設存在單向函數或牢不可破的加密，則任何屬於'''IP'''（已證等於'''[[PSPACE|PSPACE]]'''）的問題，皆有零知識證明。換言之，任何命題若可藉交互系統證明，則可零知識證明。<ref>Russell Impagliazzo, Moti Yung: Direct Minimum-Knowledge Computations. CRYPTO 1987: 40-51</ref><ref>{{cite book |first1=Michael |last1=Ben-Or |first2=Oded |last2=Goldreich |first3=Shafi |last3=Goldwasser |first4=Johan |last4=Hastad |first5=Joe |last5=Kilian |first6=Silvio |last6=Micali |first7=Phillip |last7=Rogaway |chapter=Everything provable is provable in zero-knowledge |editor-first=S. |editor-last=Goldwasser |title=Advances in Cryptology—CRYPTO '88 |volume=403 |series=Lecture Notes in Computer Science |pages=37–56 |publisher=Springer-Verlag |year=1990 }}</ref>

許多理論家不希望假設不必要的條件，所以試圖在不假定[[單向函數|單向函數]]的條件之下，證明同樣的結論。有種做法稱為「多證明者交互式證明系統」（見[[交互式证明系统|交互式证明系统]]），即有多個獨立的證明者，而非僅得一個。驗證者可以將證明者逐個孤立，然後詰問，以免被作弊證明者誤導。無需任何難解假設，已可證明在此系統中，任何'''NP'''問題皆有零知識證明。<ref>{{cite journal |first1=M. |last1=Ben-or |first2=Shafi |last2=Goldwasser |first3=J. |last3=Kilian |first4=A. |last4=Wigderson |url=http://theory.lcs.mit.edu/~cis/pubs/shafi/1988-stoc-bgkw.pdf |title=Multi prover interactive proofs: How to remove intractability assumptions |journal=Proceedings of the 20th ACM Symposium on Theory of Computing |pages=113–121 |year=1988 |access-date=2021-11-27 |archive-date=2007-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070417142744/http://theory.lcs.mit.edu/~cis/pubs/shafi/1988-stoc-bgkw.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

後來發現，互聯網等同時執行多個協議的環境中，較難構造零知識證明。研究並行零知識證明的先驅是{{link-en|辛西婭·德沃克|Cynthia Dwork}}<!--譯名見諸[[伯納德·德沃克|伯納德·德沃克]]-->、{{link-en|莫尼·納奧爾|Moni Naor}}<!--按[[WP:外語譯音表/希伯來語|WP:外語譯音表/希伯來語]]-->、{{link-en|阿米特·薩海|Amit Sahai}}。<ref>{{cite journal |first1=Cynthia |last1=Dwork |first2=Moni |last2=Naor |first3=Amit |last3=Sahai |title=Concurrent Zero Knowledge |journal=Journal of the ACM |volume=51 |issue=6 |pages=851–898 |year=2004 |doi=10.1145/1039488.1039489 |citeseerx=10.1.1.43.716 |s2cid=52827731 }}</ref>此類研究之中，重要成果有{{link-en|證據不可辨|witness-indistinguishable proof}}協議。與零知識相比，其性質較弱：可能有多種證據供證明者選擇採用何者作證，此時僅要求驗證者無法分辨證明者選擇為何{{註|即無法分辨該證明者與採用另一證據的證明者。}}，但證明者可以泄漏部分資訊，如全體證據組成的集合。儘管失去零知識性質，但此類協議的好處是，並行時不會遇到此前提及的問題。<ref>{{cite book |first1=Uriel |last1=Feige |first2=Adi |last2=Shamir |title=Witness Indistinguishable and Witness Hiding Protocols |url=https://archive.org/details/proceedingsoftwe0000acms |journal=Proceedings of the Twenty-second Annual ACM Symposium on Theory of Computing (STOC) |pages=[https://archive.org/details/proceedingsoftwe0000acms/page/416 416]–426 |year=1990 |doi=10.1145/100216.100272 |isbn=978-0897913614 |citeseerx=10.1.1.73.3911 |s2cid=11146395 }}</ref>

變式尚有{{link-en|非交互式零知識證明|non-interactive zero-knowledge proof}}。[[曼纽尔·布卢姆|曼纽尔·布卢姆]]、保羅·費爾德曼（{{lang|en|Paul Feldman}}）、米卡利證明，若證明者與驗證者共有一條隨機字串，則可以達成計算零知識，而毋須交互。<ref name="noninteractive" /><ref name="noninteractive2" />
